               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was in Laurence Pountney-lane, and saw the box laying under a window - I took it up, and heard the cry of Stop thief! I ran a little way, and immediately flung it away; I saw an officer following me, and immediately stopped for him to take me.</p>
